\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"我個gym係屋企對面馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都懶"},{"pid":"6756402a5bb50a282ad98d9fbb3966b2dec88e6b","tid":806571,"uid":9763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:55:11.000Z","msg":"我就覺得咁早做咁高強度運動好困難<br />\n倒不如早少少起身 整份精神早餐<br />\n加50下push up同郁下個人<br />\n平時食野盡量清d 少甜<br />\n放假先去跑步<br />\n叫慢慢調整下個生活<br />\n以前做廚返1200-2200都係咁上下"},{"pid":"899a65a411307b597f7e4cd271017b84c5e1212a","tid":806571,"uid":13718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"早一個鐘起身做gym <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 試咗幾日，番工好精神，但係夜晚十一點開始冇電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85cb8c17b75a85e5936a0315012ebe026758821","tid":806571,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"唯有放工做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7779b99df45c2ecdd0833938748aff4d36674e78","tid":806571,"uid":47183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"[member]樓主你份工已經fail左一大半<br />\n利申 每日6點起身做運動之後返工 準時收工 夜晚10點訓 一星期做5-6日<br />\n好醒神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [\\member]"},{"pid":"acd7ce2f1e57d4e950afc52a9e146e5c99d8cad1","tid":806571,"uid":84871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7779b99df45c2ecdd0833938748aff4d36674e78","tid":806571,"uid":47183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"[member]樓主你份工已經fail左一大半<br />\n利申 每日6點起身做運動之後返工 準時收工 夜晚10點訓 一星期做5-6日<br />\n好醒神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [\\member]"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ceb4181110a7d48c39bf5af7daa98571ff6aa4e","tid":806571,"uid":14979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:35:05.000Z","msg":"而家我係做完運動先番工<br />\n全靠前幾個月有大假去左泰國學左一個星期泰拳<br />\n個陣日日都keep住操<br />\n番到黎香港就會覺得有日唔做運動會好唔慣<br />\n同埋你見到自己有啲成果就會好有心繼續架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb65d370ef9e9a571e1f66425ac41194ae456c26","tid":806571,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb728a3ae0d40d07f1fb3bbdc3cd7de861246a6f","tid":806571,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:40:37.000Z","msg":"屋企尖東大約1個鐘<br />\n尖東9點返工 (遲到9點半都無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n有諗過九龍公園泳池游完水再返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:51:11.000Z","msg":"Rich"},{"pid":"5e40c5f8dba5714c3a68592bf3e1c96e595c61a9","tid":806571,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:54:53.000Z","msg":"運動完番工會好精神<br />\n試過就會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9a43a763a94a2a711e3773c236bf6d372319b0","tid":806571,"uid":138803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"之前早平時個半鐘起身去gym<br />\n跑30分鐘+梳洗+化妝<br />\n翻工嗰時精神咗<br />\n然後夜晚一定會訓到因爲早起<br />\n<br />\n好多人話運動完會好攰，我諗有兩樣野要注意<br />\n1.運動係習慣，好多人話跑幾多都唔係一下子，你可以試下自己幾時開始攰，可以15-20分鐘再慢慢加，養成習慣<br />\n<br />\n2.強度唔需要好攰，其實做到有少少攰，個心跳上升咗，我覺得已經ok，假設你日日跑20分鐘，會愈嚟愈唔攰，到到20分鐘你覺得輕鬆先再加時間<br />\n<br />\n飲食方面戒糖好有效，不過好多人捱唔到"}]}